        <Parent_String>Cubist [300021495], modern European fine arts styles and movements [300021494], modern European styles and movements [300021424], European [300020656], styles, periods, and cultures by region [300111079], Styles and Periods (hierarchy name) [300015646], Styles and Periods Facet [300264088]</Parent_String>
